About DevFest Berlin

Workshops

Half day of workshops, hands-on experience, hacking and debugging. Come and tame your favourite technology!

Conference

The biggest Google related event in the country carefully crafted for you by GDG community! Awesome speakers and lots of fun!

Hackathon

Full-day freestyle hackathon! Want some real team building on friday? Grab your team and join our hackathon!
